00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,880
He didn't complain about it.

290
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,960
Why are you feeling aggrieved?

291
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,360
It's not what I mean.

292
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,080
We all know

293
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,920
the captain should be credited

294
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,320
for the investigation of the case.

295
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,080
Unexpectedly,

296
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,480
the inspector pushed himself forward.

297
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,080
In my opinion,

298
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,360
the captain is a little bit silly.

299
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,960
Shut up.

300
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,680
I know the captain treats us well.

301
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:10,720
If he was not here,

302
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,240
I would have left the station house

303
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,000
years ago.

304
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,840
But I have to feed my family.

305
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,720
Right?

306
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,960
Take the checking of household registration,

307
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,840
we couldn't

308
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,640
accept nothing from householders.

309
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:20,160
It would never happen

310
00:13:20,160 --> 00:13:20,960
in any other station houses.

311
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:21,800
If he insists on doing this,

312
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,640
I'll quit.

313
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,400
Get out of here if you want to give it up.

314
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,880
I'm not targeting you.

315
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:27,680
What the hell are you yelling at?

316
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:29,320
I knew clearly

317
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,680
what you thought.

318
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:31,440
You attempted to

319
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,840
let your brother wear the police uniform.

320
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,000
But he was kicked out

321
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,160
by these raw recruits.

322
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,720
I feel embarrassed for you.

323
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:39,960
Don't you dare to say it again?

324
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:42,240
Shame on you!

325
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:43,440
Shut up!

326
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,360
[Stop fighting. We are colleagues.]

327
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,000
Let go!

328
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,280
Li.

329
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:50,560
Don't fight.

330
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,560
Stop it.

331
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:53,440
That's enough.

332
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,240
Li.

333
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:56,840
Li, stop it.

334
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:57,920
Let go.

335
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,000
Damn you.

336
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:02,600
Li, stop it.

337
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,160
Bai.

338
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:04,720
Move away.

339
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:06,440
Bai.

340
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:10,040
I'm done

341
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:11,120
and I quit.

342
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,000
So do I, Bai.

343
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,360
Tell the captain I'm sorry.

344
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,080
Wait for me, Li.

345
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:14,560
You have made yourself stand out.

346
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:15,840
I'm feeling so happy

347
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,720
for you.

348
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:18,720
I won't go there.

349
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,240
My aspiration is to serve as a policeman.

350
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,560
Nonsense.

351
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,080
Mr. Jin

352
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:26,360
is a tycoon.

353
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,800
He is a rich man.

354
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,840
If you do the personal bodyguard for him,

355
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,120
your salary a month would be

356
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:34,360
worth that of half a year in a station house.

357
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,680
You helped him to break a case.

358
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:37,680
That's why you're offered such a good job.

359
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:38,560
Cherish this opportunity.

360
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,200
They offer me a job.

361
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,600
Why do you go with me?

362
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,720
You know why.

363
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,600
You always

364
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,360
pull a long face

365
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,360
and have no talking skills.

366
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:46,960
Just stand there

367
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,120
like a statue.

368
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,440
You need my help there.

369
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,080
No.

370
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,800
Today is the day for new recruits.

371
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,440
As an inspector, you should greet them.

372
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,440
Just a bunch of inferior students.

373
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,320
Let them wait there.

374
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,360
Think about it.

375
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,960
Out of a total of 98 cadets admitted,

376
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,560
we got those at the bottom of the list, again.

377
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,480
If only we could get

378
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,520
those of top 90.

379
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:07,280
I heard

380
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,080
one of them didn't even get through

381
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,240
the admission line but still was admitted.

382
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,480
Guess what,

383
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:12,480
maybe this back-door student has

384
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:14,480
some true skills and genuine knowledge.

385
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:15,680
I was told that

386
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,600
he got full scores

387
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,080
in two subject exams

388
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,360
but missed the last one in the end.

389
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,320
Otherwise,

390
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,200
he would get through the admission line.

391
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,200
The streetcar is coming.

392
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,120
I'm not going.

393
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,080
You have to.

394
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,440
Easy, easy.

395
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,640
Let's go.

396
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:28,240
Zuo.

397
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,720
Get in.

398
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:32,480
"Carp jumps over the dragon gate"

399
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,680
If he is like what you said,

400
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:35,000
he didn't need somebody to back-door him.

401
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,840
I reckon his scores are fake.

402
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:41,720
What's his name?

403
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:45,200
I don't care his name.

404
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,600
Listen up.

405
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,200
Now we are on the way

406
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,000
to a French high-class restaurant.

407
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,320
Take care of your appearance and behavior.

408
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,840
If you were appreciated someday,

409
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,840
that would be my honor.

410
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,360
Got it.

411
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,840
Look at the girl by that door.

412
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,600
She is really pretty.

413
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,200
Which one?

414
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:02,880
The one in the front.

415
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,200
Well...

416
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:11,080
You are 29 years old.

417
00:17:11,080 --> 00:17:12,360
You are not a child.

418
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:24,800
Excuse me.

419
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:26,600
I want to put up a missing person notice.

420
00:17:26,600 --> 00:17:27,560
Come over.

421
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:30,560
What do you want to post?

422
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:31,200
Here.

423
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:34,880
You want to find your teacher?

424
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,560
[I wish all bridges]

425
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,960
[and all tunnels your pass be firm and bright.]

426
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,240
From whom?

427
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:40,840
No name.

428
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:42,720
You don't leave a name on it.

429
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,200
How should he know you are after him?

430
00:17:46,080 --> 00:17:46,960
He will.

431
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:47,480
Thank you.

432
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:51,600
Chen Hao.

433
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:57,320
Chen Hao.

434
00:17:57,320 --> 00:17:58,840
Where are you?

435
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,240
Come out.

436
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:02,960
Stop it.

437
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:03,840
He didn't come back.

438
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:06,240
What's wrong with you?

439
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,800
You are looking upset.

440
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:09,560
Li and Shitou quitted.

441
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:13,840
What can I say?

442
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:15,080
They would quit anyway.

443
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:18,360
We need fresh blood.

444
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:21,600
You got married in this suit?

445
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:24,560
Line up.

446
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:26,120
Attention!

447
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,840
Let me introduce

448
00:18:35,840 --> 00:18:37,320
this man standing in front of you.

449
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:38,040
He is the police inspector

450
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:39,360
of the Fourth Station House

451
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:41,120
of the Shiliupu Police Station

452
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:43,200
of the Police Department.

453
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:44,480
Zuo Ronghua.

454
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:46,960
You may clap.

455
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,360
At ease.

456
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,320
We can be like a family.

457
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,480
From now on,

458
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:58,000
just call me Zuo.

459
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:00,080
The station house has a bad reputation.

460
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,720
But I don't think so.

461
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,720
I can feel its warmth.

462
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,120
Just like a big family.

463
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:09,000
Hence,

464
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,200
I hope everyone of you

465
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,960
will make the station house

466
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,120
your another big family.

467
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:14,000
I think

468
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,080
it's better to introduce yourself first.

469
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:18,560
Talk about why you want to be a policeman.

470
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:20,440
Who will be the first?

471
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:20,960
I will.

472
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:21,720
I will.

473
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:22,120
OK.

474
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,360
Sir,

475
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:26,800
my name is Sun Hongfa.

476
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,320
My father is the owner

477
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:28,800
of the Hongfa Restaurant.

478
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:29,200
My uncle

479
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,120
and Chief Wang of the Fifth Baojia District

480
00:19:30,120 --> 00:19:31,000
are sworn brothers.

481
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,240
This is my family's business card.

482
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:34,600
Here you are.

483
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,280
Good.

484
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,000
My family wanted me

485
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,120
to serve in government.

486
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:41,120
But I persisted in serving in the police force.

487
00:19:41,120 --> 00:19:41,840
Because it is my dream

488
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:43,600
to become a policeman.

489
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:45,120
Great!

490
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,560
My name is Tian Dongbao.

491
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:49,440
I did chicken raising in the countryside.

492
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,840
But my father didn't want me to do that.

493
00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:52,480
He told me a policeman would be paid more

494
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,800
than a chicken breeder.

495
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:55,440
Good.

496
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,760
You can breed some chickens

497
00:19:56,760 --> 00:19:57,880
in our station house

498
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,000
to improve our food diversity.

499
00:19:59,000 --> 00:19:59,240
And...

500
00:19:59,240 --> 00:19:59,800
Yes, sir.

501
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,040
So the pretty girl.

502
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:05,360
Why do you serve in the police force?

503
00:20:05,360 --> 00:20:06,360
Sir,

504
00:20:06,360 --> 00:20:07,160
I want to do the cause

505
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:09,160
because I want to protect my family.

506
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:11,320
That sounds interesting.

507
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:13,520
You are Luo...

508
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:14,360
Luo Minmin.

509
00:20:14,360 --> 00:20:15,040
Oh, yes.

510
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:15,840
I know you.

511
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:16,720
You are the last one

512
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,640
on the admission list.

513
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:21,040
Don't feel embarrassed.

514
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:22,560
Their scores

515
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:23,800
are almost the same as yours.

516
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:25,520
It is so wonderful

517
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:27,320
to have a policewoman here.

518
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:29,280
You don't need to do field operations

519
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:30,920
because that is a waste of your talent.

520
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,440
When guests or superiors

521
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:34,040
visit the station house,

522
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:35,600
you are responsible for

523
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,600
greeting

524
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:38,040
and serving them.

525
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:40,360
So that's it.

526
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,520
This young man

527
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:46,800
has a good figure

528
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:47,800
and appearance.

529
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:48,840
Pretty good.

530
00:20:50,080 --> 00:20:51,360
What's it for to join the police force?

531
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,240
the Chairman said

532
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,040
police force must be the base of a country.

533
00:20:59,080 --> 00:21:01,080
A policeman must uphold justice

534
00:21:01,080 --> 00:21:02,280
and protect people.

535
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:08,760
[That bad man is a policeman.]

536
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:11,360
[He wears a police cap and a uniform.]

537
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,880
Why do you take an English book with you?

538
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:22,880
That tall man

539
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:25,040
is the guy in place of Bai's brother

540
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,640
through a back-door dealing.

541
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,280
Let me introduce this man.

542
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:32,120
This is the captain of our station house.

543
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:33,000
Chen Hao.

544
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,360
He will be in charge of

545
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:35,440
your specific duties.

546
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:36,920
Say something.

547
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,840
I need to get changed.

548
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:50,640
We met before.

549
00:21:51,840 --> 00:21:52,400
Do you remember?

550
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:56,840
Yes.

551
00:21:58,040 --> 00:21:58,920
What is your name?

552
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:01,520
Xiang Yuansheng.

553
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,240
X-i-a-n-g Xiang?

554
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:11,840
Y-u-a-n Yuan

555
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:12,920
and s-h-e-n-g sheng.

556
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:24,800
I'm your captain.

557
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:25,800
My name is Chen Hao.

558
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:27,520
You are going to

559
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:29,680
do a one-month-long internship.

560
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,880
You will be divided into two groups.

561
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,760
Two men in each group.

562
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:33,520
If you pass the exam,

563
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:34,800
you will become a regular policeman.

564
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:36,320
Otherwise, you will be fired.

565
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:37,160
Understand?

566
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,120
Yes, sir.

567
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:39,920
Now choose your partner.

568
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:41,440
Captain.

569
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:43,840
I want him with me in a group.

570
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:46,160
OK, approved.

571
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,040
Sir.

572
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:52,320
I have a request.

573
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,120
Speak.

574
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:54,520
I want to go on field operations with them.

575
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:55,360
Do you agree?

576
00:22:56,360 --> 00:22:57,600
Why did you say that?

577
00:22:57,600 --> 00:22:59,840
The inspector asked me

578
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:00,760
to greet and serve guests

579
00:23:00,760 --> 00:23:01,840
and superiors.

580
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:02,640
No policewoman ever worked here

581
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:04,000
before.

582
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,520
So it was awkward

583
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:05,760
to arrest female criminals.

584
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,240
You are the first one coming here.

585
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:08,840
