Next time,

885
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:20,280
don't use violence.

886
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:22,120
So...

887
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:24,120
What is the office's name?

888
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:28,640
Officer Xiang.

889
00:39:29,640 --> 00:39:30,800
Goodbye, Officer Xiang.

890
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:18,920
Zuo.

891
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:21,640
Who is behind him?

892
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:24,520
Do you mean Xiang Yuansheng?

893
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:31,120
You didn't know anything.

894
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:33,200
I asked.

895
00:40:33,200 --> 00:40:34,200
But it looked weird.

896
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:35,440
Nobody told me.

897
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:39,280
But you have reminded me.

898
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,640
I often heard rustlings

899
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:42,800
in the yard.

900
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:43,640
Is there a rat in the house?

901
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:46,640
Can you get a cat?

902
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,640
Get one for me.

903
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:51,560
Cats always come after rats.

904
00:40:52,520 --> 00:40:53,880
What do you mean?

905
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:55,120
Just keep him.

906
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:57,640
Let's observe what he attempts to do.

907
00:40:57,640 --> 00:40:59,000
What?

908
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:01,560
Rats are rats.

909
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:03,240
They feed on birds.

910
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,720
Why are you laughing?

911
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,760
Have some more.

912
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,840
You have a big appetite.

913
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:34,360
Here.

914
00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:36,120
Thank you.

915
00:41:41,160 --> 00:41:41,720
Thank you.

916
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:49,000
Have more.

917
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:52,840
You don't have to thank me.

918
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:55,760
It's quite normal

919
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,960
on your first day.

920
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,360
Actually,

921
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:01,640
I want to ask you a question.

922
00:42:02,200 --> 00:42:03,320
Did I look embarrassed

923
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:05,160
just now?

924
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:08,360
What?

925
00:42:09,040 --> 00:42:10,480
I know

926
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,240
I damaged the image of the police force.

927
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:13,480
I was at the bottom

928
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:14,800
of the admission list,

929
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:15,960
narrowly made it.

930
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:17,320
If someone was weeded out,

931
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:18,480
it would be me.

932
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:19,640
But I'm determined to

933
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:20,840
stay here.

934
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,120
Therefore,

935
00:42:23,120 --> 00:42:24,480
from now on,

936
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,360
I wish

937
00:42:25,360 --> 00:42:26,680
we could help each other.

938
00:42:29,040 --> 00:42:29,720
So

939
00:42:29,720 --> 00:42:30,120
allow me to introduce myself

940
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:31,960
to you.

941
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,280
My name is Luo Minmin.

942
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:34,920
If you get in trouble

943
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:35,960
in future,

944
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,040
I can help you.

945
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,280
I heard

946
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:43,040
you are the one getting the job through back-door dealings,

947
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:43,560
right?

948
00:42:45,240 --> 00:42:45,840
Yes.

949
00:42:46,680 --> 00:42:47,200
You surely

950
00:42:47,200 --> 00:42:48,360
understand my feeling,

951
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:48,880
right?

952
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,920
So let's call it a deal.

953
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:55,800
Thank you for helping me out.

954
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:57,880
We are partners,

955
00:42:57,880 --> 00:42:58,400
right?

956
00:43:02,960 --> 00:43:03,880
If possible,

957
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:05,320
I advise you

958
00:43:05,320 --> 00:43:06,480
to change a partner as soon as possible!

959
00:43:19,960 --> 00:43:21,120
I don't get it.

960
00:43:21,120 --> 00:43:22,160
What a strange man!
